docs/api-reference.md:3435:Runs preconditions; on any failure, returns `precondition_failed` with no mutation or event applied. Otherwise applies every buffered mutation in registration order via the corresponding public `World` API (so mutations get the same liveness, bounds, and JSON-compat validation as direct calls), then emits every buffered event via `world.emit`. Returns the success result with counts.
